staircase and less quiet.

An easily accessible, secure, furnished second floor Puncak Menggatal unit for immediate rent.

name: Rey
body:
Pangsapuri Filantus Bandar Baru Bangi
Selangor - Bangi
==========
RM 1 200
(per month)
==========
Pangsapuri Filantus fully furnished berkonsep moden dan kemas pastinya sangat berbaloi kepada golongan pelajar atau keluarga kecil yang ingin kediaman sudah lengkap dengan barangan dekor yang cantik.

Rumah ini telah dihiaskan oleh jenama syarikat ID popular Projek MakeOver Interior Design bagi memberi keselesaan kepada anda yang ingin menyewa di kediaman ini.

KENAPA PILIH PREMIS INI:
1. Ruang dalaman rumah yang cantik, dihias lengkap dengan barangan rumah seperti gambar tersedia

2. Mempunyai 3 Bilik tidur lengkap dengan katil, tilam, cadar, bantal, karpet, ruang gantung pakaian, meja sisi dan lampu meja serta langsir

3. Bilik air x1 dan tandas x1 yang bersih serta mempunyai kekuatan air paip yang kuat dan puas untuk membersihkan diri dan barangan peribadi

4. Lokasi strategik di Teras Jernang Bandar Baru Bangi. Berdekatan dengan Universiti ternama seperti UKM, GMI Universiti, KPTM Bangi. Dekat dengan kawasan pusat bandar seperti Bandar Baru Bangi, Putrajaya, Cyberjaya, Kajang serta KLIA.

5. kediaman lengkap dengan dekor lengkap ruang tamu dan ruang makan, mempunya aircond 1.5hp di ruang tamu, barangan lengkap keperluan bilik tidur di semua bilik dan tandas, mempunyai rak terbuka serta peti sejuk di dapur kering, airfryer dan meja konkrit di dapur basah. Pili air juga mempunyai tekanan air yang kuat, sangat selesa menggunakan pili air.

6. Ada satu lot parkir kereta berbumbung untuk premis ini. Selain itu kawasan parkir terbuka juga banyak dengan syarat parkir dengan berhemah.


SANGAT SESUAI UNTUK ANDA YANG:
1. Pelajar yang ingin ruang privacy, tinggal dalam group kecil seperti 6 orang dan ingin kediaman yang lengkap dan cantik (Masuk bawa pakaian dah boleh terus diami)

2. Yang mempunyai keluarga kecil dan tidak mahu barang sarat dan ingin semua barang tersedia supaya senang nak plan suatu hari nanti dah ada kediaman sendiri

3. Yang ingin mendapatkan bilik secara privacy dan ingin mencari penyewa tambahan untuk sewakan bilik yang lain


Harga Promosi
RM1200/ bulan

BAYARAN PERTAMA UNTUK MASUK KE KEDIAMAN
RM1200 (Bulanan Pertama) + RM2400 (Deposit dua bulan) + RM1000 (Deposit Utiliti dua bulan)
= RM4600.00

* Ada kontrak penyewa dan pemilik kediaman
* Minimum tinggal adalah dua tahun, kurang maaf kami tidak ambil
* Untuk penyewa pembersih, boleh jaga barangan kediaman dan Muslim sahaja
* Tidak mahu penyewa bermasalah pembayaran. Cakap jelas-jelas dan awal-awal senang tak nak nanti isu di masa akan datang.

* Tertakluk terma dan syarat

Looking for a move-in ready, stylish, and well-maintained home in a prime location? This beautifully furnished unit is now available for rent and is perfect for working professionals, expatriates, or couples seeking comfort, convenience, and a welcoming space to call home.

Comfortable bedrooms, Master bedroom with Coway mattress

Furniture and appliances as shown in the photos

Curtains and light fixtures

Monthly maintenance fee covered by the owner (negotiable yearly)

The unit offers easy access to key highways, public transportation, commercial hubs, international schools, shopping malls and medical facilities (next to Columbia Asia PJ Hospital). Whether you're commuting to work or exploring the city, you'll appreciate the convenience this address offers.

Casa Indah 2 is a beautifully designed and a unique leasehold development located in Persiaran Surian, Kota Damansara, Selangor near Petaling Jaya. The construction of this project was done by a famous development company known as the Damansara Impian which is a subsidiary company of the Dijaya Group Corporation. The development of this project was completed in the year 2008. It is considered to be a great addition in the Selangor property. The property is going to boom in the future, making it ideal from an investment perspective.

Casa Indah 2 is indeed a great place to live in. The development offers many great facilities and features that the residents of many new developments only dream of having. The residents of the development can enjoy a beautiful nursery in the development and enjoy some fresh environment in the development. There is a mini market in the development from where the residents can spend some unforgettable time with their family and friends. Multipurpose hall is also available in the development which can be used on different occasions by the residents. The development company did not forget about the children and has developed a lovely childrenâ€™s playground in the area where the children can enjoy while remaining in the development and without worrying the parents.

Casa Indah 2 was developed strategically keeping in mind the importance of accessibility of the location. The residents do not have to worry about moving to and from the location even if they do not have their own vehicles. The development is easily accessible via LDP, NKVE and Penchala Link. Public transportation is also available in the area and the residents of the development can use the Taman Paramount LRT Station, Taman Bahagia LRT Station and Kelana Jaya LRT Station to move to any place in the city. Furthermore, taxis and buses to move to and from the location easily. Other than its strategic location, the area is surrounded with plenty of amenities. The residents do not have to worry about anything in the area because everything is easily available in the locality. Educational institutions such as Honsbridge Academy, Smart Reader Kids, Little Kingdom and SEGi University College are just a short distance away from the development. There are many shopping spots as well near the development and few of the famous shopping spots near the development are namely Sunway Giza Mall, 7-Eleven and Pasar Segar Fresh Eden from where the residents can shop for almost anything they want. Furthermore, there are many eateries, mosques, petrol stations, churches and hospitals as well in the area, making sure that the residents of the development do not have to worry about anything.

Casa Indah 2 provides other facilities and features as well, such as a swimming pool and a great gymnasium equipped with latest exercising machines where the residents can work out while remaining in the development and enjoy a healthy lifestyle. The development also provides complete parking facility for its residents. Most importantly, the development is equipped with modern security gadgets and provides 24 hour security to its residents to make sure that the residents are protected from any kind of external threats while they are in the development.

This is a 1-Bedroom Garden Studio flat unit in this most sought after, secure area of Luyang Lintas, Hilltop , Foh sang , Damai.
